title: Atlantis Evolution
description:
Adventure game from Dreamcatcher. It&#039;s the yar 1904. On his way back to New York, Curtis Hewitt, a young adventurer and photographer, is caught in a vortex that sends him to the heart of the lost city of Atlantis. A stranger in a land of hi-tech and archaic faith, Curtis endures thrilling adventure helping the people of Atlantis overthrow the mighty "Atlantian" Gods. 

The game features full-screen 3D graphics, showing off five fascinating destinations that players can explore, each with its own culture and mysteries. Like most games in the genre, Atlantis Evolution promises many diverse challenging puzzles and games and is complemented by a beautiful and captivating original soundtrack.
